dc_title_s: Plan de la ville et des faubourgs de Paris, divisé en ses vingt quartiers; par le Sr. Robert de Vaugondy.
dc_description_s: Includes indexes. Color outlines the cité, ville, and univers. 1 map: hand col.; 49 x 61 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
